\tan{(\alpha + 45^\circ)} = \frac{AB}{AC} = \frac{\frac{x}{\sqrt{2}}+120}{\frac{x}{\sqrt{2}}} = \frac{\frac{x+120\sqrt{2}}{\sqrt{2}}}{\frac{x}{\sqrt{2}}} = \frac{x+120\sqrt{2}}{{x}} = 1 + \frac{120\sqrt{2}}{x}
